                                                                 TripQuery tripQuery)
        Find the best waypoint order using TSP based on a list of participating JoinTripRequest for an TripOffer and a TripQuery from a passenger that wants to join this trip.
        Parameters:
        joinTripRequests - all join requests that should be considered, regardless of what state they are in
        tripOffer - route information for the driver
        tripQuery - additional way points that should be considered
        Returns:
        all possible routes sorted by their air distance (shortes first)
